  "detailed_description": "<strong>Amortizer</strong> is a casual off-road experience.<br>You will find your self in various nature environment, driving 4x4 machine.<br>Game does not have any progress. Its made for true off-road lovers. <br>You have seven linear maps to complete, without hurry.<br><br>Be prepared for mudy,rocky,sandy,snowy environment. <br>Prove that you can sustain in all circumstances.<br>Sit back and enjoy the bumpy ride.<br>After that you can scout around in two open world maps.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- Realistic Physics<br>- Deformable Terrain<br>- Various Natural Environments<br>- 9 Levels (7 linear levels to complete and 2 medium size open world maps)",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Amortizer</strong> is a casual off-road experience.<br>You will find your self in various nature environment, driving 4x4 machine.<br>Game does not have any progress. Its made for true off-road lovers. <br>You have seven linear maps to complete, without hurry.<br><br>Be prepared for mudy,rocky,sandy,snowy environment. <br>Prove that you can sustain in all circumstances.<br>Sit back and enjoy the bumpy ride.<br>After that you can scout around in two open world maps.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- Realistic Physics<br>- Deformable Terrain<br>- Various Natural Environments<br>- 9 Levels (7 linear levels to complete and 2 medium size open world maps)",
